text: O'Hara Township is a township with home rule statusPennsylvania Code Title 302, Section 21.1-101 et seq. in Allegheny County, Pennsylvania in the United States. It is six miles northeast of Downtown Pittsburgh. The population was 9,284 at the 2020 census. ==References== Category:Townships in Allegheny County, Pennsylvania
title: O'Hara Township, Allegheny County, Pennsylvania
